{{Top|leg}}
'''Sigma group''' was a standard designation for [[Delta-class DX-9 stormtrooper transport|''Delta''-class DX-9 stormtrooper transports]] found aboard [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] warships or [[Space station/Legends|space stations]].

A typical duty for these craft was disabling and boarding enemy craft, such as the [[BFF-1 bulk freighter/Legends|BFF-1 bulk freighter]] [[Onece group|''Onece'']], or [[Proton rocket/Legends|heavy rocket]] attack such as the assault on the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] cruiser [[Lulsla (MC40a light cruiser)|''Lulsla'']].

Another standard designation for Imperial DX-9s was ''[[Omega]]''.

